"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)、華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)、群益優選非投等債 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00953B:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00953B\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00953B-TW</a>)、台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
